S.FORM: == navenaquan nua kiukay == kiukay a navenaquan saka papetemalidu tua nasi nua taqaljaqaljan i kacauan. azua nanguaqan kata zua parkivalisakesaked a kinasicuai nua taqaljaqaljan i kacauan, kemalja mapasusuan angata. saka azua namaljekuyanga , azua naseveric anga itua seizi a bungka, kai, senai, etc mapacikel, masanpazangel a mumalj i kiukay. Taiwan Kiristu Ciuru Kiukay Patjezalemanen i Qinaljan tua Saluan ayaya a pakisamulja tua sinzia a Taiwan Kiristu Ciuru Kiukay. nukuya inika tja sanpazangalen a bungka nua marka martimaljimalji a kinataqaljaqaljan my paseljayar tua patjara Cemas. nu pupatarevan itjen, azua kaizuan bungka mavan a tjlja paravacan a turivecan nu lihai a kiukay. mavan tua nu sika pakaizua tua kinacalisianan a Siisiu, qau azua Siisiu a kinacalisianan mavan anga tjlja kudrulan tua namasan kinituayan tua kai a bungka nua kacalisian. kiukay i Paiwan nu seman patarevan itjen tua kiukay i Paiwan zuku, a kakasizuan a tatuluan tua patjara kinacalisianan i kiukay nu aya, tjlja maljaluyan a kai, senai kata zua papaqaljian nua caucau. tjuruvu maqacuvucuvung a macaqu a lemangda, a qivu, a semupu tua kai a Pinaiwanan, a macaqu a semenai tua senai a kinacalisianan, kiukay a pakaizua tua kituluan a sinikacaqu, qau izua "kakimadjuan a kituluan" saka izua uta a "pinaranaw a semavuta a pakitulu".

== navenaqoan noa kiokay == kiokay a navenaqoan saka papetemalido toa nasi noa taqaljaqaljan i kacaoan. azoa nangoaqan kata zoa parkivalisakesaked a kinasicoai noa taqaljaqaljan i kacaoan, kemalja mapasosoan angata. saka azoa namaljekoyanga , azoa naseveric anga itoa seizi a bongka, kai, senai, etc mapacikel, masanpazangel a momalj i kiokay. Taiwan Kiristo Cioro Kiokay Patjezalemanen i Qinaljan toa Saloan ayaya a pakisamolja toa sinzia a Taiwan Kiristo Cioro Kiokay. nokoya inika tja sanpazangalen a bongka noa marka martimaljimalji a kinataqaljaqaljan my paseljayar toa patjara Cemas. no popatarevan itjen, azoa kaizoan bongka mavan a tjlja paravacan a torivecan no lihai a kiokay. mavan toa no sika pakaizoa toa kinacalisianan a Siisio, qao azoa Siisio a kinacalisianan mavan anga tjlja kodrolan toa namasan kinitoayan toa kai a bongka noa kacalisian. kiokay i Paiwan no seman patarevan itjen toa kiokay i Paiwan zoko, a kakasizoan a tatoloan toa patjara kinacalisianan i kiokay no aya, tjlja maljaloyan a kai, senai kata zoa papaqaljian noa caocao. tjorovo maqacovocovong a macaqo a lemangda, a qivo, a semopo toa kai a Pinaiwanan, a macaqo a semenai toa senai a kinacalisianan, kiokay a pakaizoa toa kitoloan a sinikacaqo, qao izoa "kakimadjoan a kitoloan" saka izoa ota a "pinaranaw a semavota a pakitolo".
